Adds a camp location near Dawnstar. There is also an interesting book I wrote. Edward Lewis, the author of the book (in game) will return to his home in Skyrim at one point. He has started the huge rumor about the mysterious pack. No one has seen a werewolf in Skyrim for at least 500 years, but will anyone come across a werewolf from the Omega Pack?  WARNING THIS ONLY ADDS A CAMP! NO QUESTS ARE INCLUDED YET!

IF YOU WANT THE REAL DEAL OF MY MOD GO TO THIS LINK: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=763938396

THE MOD ON HERE IS UNSUPPORTED MEANING IT IS UNSTABLE! USE THE STEAM COMMUNITY LINK FOR THE LATEST VERSIONS! IT ALSO UPDATES AUTOMATICALLY!
